ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
PrecisAppointment of ROSEMARY CAPPARELLI of Kirkland, Quebec, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Allan Duncan Rowe, whose term has expired.
